column2: SELECT TOP # p.apstar_id, p.apogee_id, p.ra, p.dec, p.glon, p.glat, p.vhelio_avg, p.vscatter, a.teff, a.logg, a.m_h FROM apogeeStar p JOIN fGetNearbyApogeeStarEq (#, #, #) n on p.apstar_id = n.apstar_id JOIN aspcapStar a on a.apstar_id = p.apstar_id JOIN apogeeObject as o ON a.apogee_id = o.apogee_id AND o.j between # AND # AND o.h between # AND # AND o.k between # AND #
